====Noun====
{{en-noun}}
# Either of the [[letter]]s [[ъ]] and [[ь]] in [[Cyrillic]] [[alphabet]]s, which originally represented [[phonemic]]ally the ultra-short vowels in [[Slavic]] [[language]]s.
